#Week 11 Weekend Homework: Avocadoes

Weve looked at a few different ways in which we can build models this week, including how to prepare them properly. This weekend well build a multiple linear regression model on a dataset which will need some preparation. The data has come from Kaggle and can be found in the data folder.

We want to model avocado sales. Youll need to identify the target variable and use the tools weve worked with this week in order to prepare your dataset and find appropriate predictors. Once youve built your model use the validation techniques discussed on Wednesday to evaluate it.
